Three former SARS officials are expected to make an
appearance in Court on Monday.According to reports, former officials Ivan Pillay,
Johann van Loggerenberg and Andries Janse van Rensburg are due to appear at the
Pretoria Magistrate court on charges relating to the alleged bugging of the NPA
offices in 2007.It is reported that the charges are part of the so-called
